replies.body:
Well there are a ton more sustain options now if you want to make yourself a bit more resilient. And there are lots of AD boosting non keystone runes in domination and sorcery if you want to splash one of those instead of resolve. I don't think it is end of the world bad.

Also, there will be funny edge cases of people forgetting not to take magical footwear against you and you can chase them to death over and over
{{sticker:sg-poppy}}
